{"pageProps":{"post":{"title":"알고리즘 - 정수 내림차순으로 배치하기","date":"2020-01-10","slug":"2020-01-10-algorithm-21","content":"<h4>문제설명</h4>\n<p>함수 solution은 정수 n을 매개변수로 입력받습니다. n의 각 자릿수를 큰것부터 작은 순으로 정렬한 새로운 정수를 리턴해주세요. 예를들어 n이 118372면 873211을 리턴하면 됩니다.</p>\n<br>\n<h4>제한사항</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>n은 1이상 8000000000 이하인 자연수입니다.</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<h4>입출력 예</h4>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>n</th>\n<th>return</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>118372</td>\n<td>873211</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<br>\n<h4><strong>풀이</strong></h4>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"javascript\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">function</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">solution</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75; font-style: italic\">n</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">) {</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">var</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">answer</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">=</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">0</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">answer</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">=</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">String</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">n</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    .</span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">split</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">\"\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    .</span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">sort</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">((</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75; font-style: italic\">a</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">, </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75; font-style: italic\">b</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">) </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">=></span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">b</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">-</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">a</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    .</span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">join</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">\"\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">);</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">return</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">Number</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">answer</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">);</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<ol>\n<li>매개변수 <code>n</code>을 먼저 <code>String</code> 메소드를 사용해 문자열로 변환해준다.</li>\n<li><code>split</code> 메소드를 사용해 배열로 나눠준뒤 <code>sort</code>로 내림차순 정렬해준다.</li>\n<li><code>join</code>으로 배열을 문자열로 변환해준다.</li>\n<li>마지막으로 <code>Number</code>를 사용해 숫자로 변환해준다.</li>\n</ol>\n<br>\n<h4><strong>다른 사람 풀이</strong></h4>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"javascript\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">function</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">solution</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75; font-style: italic\">n</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">) {</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">const</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">newN</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">=</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">n</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">+</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">\"\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">const</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">newArr</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">=</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">newN</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">split</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">\"\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">).</span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">sort</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">().</span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">reverse</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">().</span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">join</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">\"\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">);</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">return</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">+</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">newArr</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<ol>\n<li>매개변수 <code>n</code>을 문자열로 변환하고 변수에 담아준다.</li>\n<li>newN를 배열로 나누고 정렬한 뒤 뒤집어주고 문자열로 변환한다.</li>\n<li>마지막으로 숫자로 변환해준다.</li>\n</ol>\n<br>\n<h4><strong>배운점</strong></h4>\n<p>첨부터 내림차순으로 정렬하면 되는데 굳이 왜 정렬 시키고 뒤집는지는 모르겠다..<br>\n그래도 내림차순엔 저렇게 뒤집을 수 있다는걸 알 수 있었다.</p>\n<p><br><br><br><br><br></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><subtitle>reference</subtitle></p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://tutorial.djangogirls.org/ko\">https://tutorial.djangogirls.org/ko</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://blog.daum.net/_blog/BlogTypeView.do?blogid=0QtKg&#x26;articleno=28&#x26;categoryId=0&#x26;totalcnt=30\">http://blog.daum.net/_blog/BlogTypeView.do?blogid=0QtKg&#x26;articleno=28&#x26;categoryId=0&#x26;totalcnt=30</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br><br><br><br><br></p>","coverImage":"/assets/blog/cover/algorithm.jpg"}},"__N_SSG":true}